%% PATIENT_MANAGEMENT Processing Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller
    participant HABADTE

    Caller->>HABADTE: Start inpatient transfer export
    HABADTE->>HABADTE: BR-017 FILE INDICATOR equals 0 branch to SKIP
    HABADTE-->>Caller: Skip account file when indicator is 0

    HABADTE->>HABADTE: BR-018 FLAG INDICATOR void or voided branch to SKIP
    HABADTE-->>HABADTE: Increment skippedVoided counter

    HABADTE->>HABADTE: BR-019 INPATIENT OUTPATIENT FLAG outpatient branch to SKIP
    HABADTE-->>HABADTE: Increment skippedOutpatient counter

    HABADTE-->>Caller: Return eligible inpatient transfers
